ZH: 我们必须克服困境，不让阻力阻碍我们前进。
EN: We must overcome obstacles and not allow resistance to impede our progress.

ZH: 运动员要面对巨大的阻力，以达到更高的速度。
EN: Athletes have to overcome enormous resistance in order to achieve higher speeds.

ZH: 这个设计有一个减少风阻的特殊形状。
EN: This design has a specific shape to reduce air resistance.

